GlobalNest - AI Design Builder Prompt

  Product Overview

  GlobalNest is an AI-powered operating system for international real estate investment. The platform connects Israeli investors with global property opportunities through AI-powered matching, a verified professional network (brokers, lawyers, mortgage advisors), and integrated transaction management. The platform is bilingual (Hebrew/English) with full RTL support.

  Target Users

  Primary:
  - First-time international investors (ages 25-45, $200K-$1M net worth)
  - Experienced investors expanding portfolios (ages 35-55, own 1-3 properties)
  - Israeli expatriates seeking Hebrew-speaking support

  Secondary:
  - Real estate professionals: brokers, lawyers, mortgage advisors seeking qualified leads

  Brand Personality

  - Trustworthy - Verified professionals, secure transactions
  - Intelligent - AI-powered, data-driven recommendations
  - Accessible - Simplifies complex international investing
  - Premium - High-quality experience for serious investors
  - Modern - Cutting-edge technology, sleek interface

  Design System Requirements

  Theme: Dark glassmorphism with premium feel

  Colors:
  - Background: Deep navy/dark slate
  - Primary accent: Amber/Gold (#F59E0B) - represents wealth, premium
  - Secondary: Cool slate tones
  - Success: Emerald
  - Text: White/off-white foreground, muted gray for secondary text

  Typography:
  - Clean, modern sans-serif
  - Clear hierarchy: Large bold headings, comfortable body text
  - Excellent readability in both Hebrew (RTL) and English (LTR)

  Components:
  - Glassmorphism cards: bg-card/30 with backdrop-blur, subtle borders
  - Rounded corners (rounded-2xl)
  - Subtle hover animations (scale, border color shifts)
  - Phosphor Icons for iconography

  Key Sections to Design

  1. Hero Section
  - Compelling headline about international real estate investing
  - Animated 3D globe visualization showing global reach
  - Clear CTA buttons: "Start Your Journey" / "For Professionals"
  - Trust indicators (verified badge, security icons)

  2. About Section
  - Company story and mission statement
  - Team introduction grid with glassmorphism cards
  - Scroll-triggered fade-in animations

  3. Features Section (Bento Grid)
  6 core features with icons:
  - AI-Powered Investor Onboarding (conversational profile building)
  - Verified Professional Network (vetted brokers, lawyers, advisors)
  - Global Property Marketplace (curated investment opportunities)
  - Unified Communication Hub (messaging, file sharing, collaboration)
  - AI Market Insights (recommendations, risk assessment, contract review)
  - Deal Room (secure transaction management)

  4. Social Proof Section
  - Key metrics display: Active Investors, Properties Listed, Countries Covered, Total Investment Volume
  - Testimonial cards with star ratings
  - "Trusted by" logo row (grayscale with hover color)

  5. How It Works (Process)
  4 steps with icons:
  1. Build Your Profile (AI chat onboarding)
  2. Get Matched (AI matches properties + professionals)
  3. Connect & Collaborate (messaging, document sharing)
  4. Close Deals (Deal Room, transaction management)

  6. FAQ Section
  - Accordion component for common questions
  - Topics: Safety, languages, costs, financing, professional quality
  - CTA below: "Still have questions? Contact us"

  7. CTA Section
  - Split appeal: Investors / Professionals
  - Strong action language
  - Sign-up form or button

  8. Footer
  - Navigation links
  - Social media
  - Legal links (Privacy, Terms)
  - Language switcher
  - Newsletter signup

  UX Requirements

  - Responsive: Mobile-first, adapts beautifully to tablet and desktop
  - Bilingual: Seamless Hebrew/English switching with proper RTL support
  - Accessibility: WCAG 2.1 AA compliant, proper contrast ratios
  - Performance: Fast loading, optimized images, lazy loading
  - Animations: Subtle, purposeful motion with Framer Motion (scroll-triggered, staggered reveals)

  Key User Flows to Consider

  Investor Flow:
  1. Land on homepage → Understand value proposition
  2. Click "Start Journey" → AI onboarding chat
  3. Complete 11-step profile → See personalized recommendations
  4. Browse marketplace → Save properties
  5. Connect with professionals → Message, share files
  6. Enter Deal Room → Complete transaction

  Professional Flow:
  1. Land on homepage → Click "For Professionals"
  2. Apply → Submit credentials for verification
  3. Get verified → Profile goes live
  4. Receive matches → Connect with qualified investors
  5. Collaborate in Deal Room → Close deals

  Content Tone

  - Confident but not arrogant
  - Educational and guiding
  - Empathetic to investor fears (trust, risk, complexity)
  - Clear and jargon-free
  - Professional with warmth

  Visual Inspiration

  - Fintech apps (premium, data-rich dashboards)
  - Proptech platforms (property visualization, maps)
  - AI assistants (conversational interfaces)
  - Trust-building design (verification badges, security indicators, reviews)